Create a program Restaurant Order System (Functions Version)

Data Types:

customer_name (string)
items (list)
prices (list)
total_price (float)
is_paid (boolean)

Functions:

def add_item(items, prices, item_name, price)

Add item_name to items list and price to prices list. Print updated items list.

def calculate_total(prices)

Calculate and return total price using the prices list.

def remove_item(items, prices, item_name)

Remove item from items list and also remove corresponding price. Print updated list.

def pay_order(is_paid)

Change payment status to True and print confirmation message.

def get_order_summary(customer_name, items, total_price, is_paid)

Return all order information in a clean format.
